  "page": "Johanna Lannister",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">Not to be confused with <a href=\"/index.php/Joanna_Lannister\" title=\"Joanna Lannister\">Joanna Lannister</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Westerling\" title=\"House Westerling\"><img alt=\"House Westerling.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/House_Westerling.svg/50px-House_Westerling.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/House_Westerling.svg/75px-House_Westerling.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f3/House_Westerling.svg/100px-House_Westerling.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Lady</span><br />Johanna Lannister</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\"><img alt=\"House Lannister.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/50px-House_Lannister.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/75px-House_Lannister.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/100px-House_Lannister.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Johanna_Lannister_Hylora.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Johanna Lannister Hylora.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/65/Johanna_Lannister_Hylora.jpg/350px-Johanna_Lannister_Hylora.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"430\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/65/Johanna_Lannister_Hylora.jpg/525px-Johanna_Lannister_Hylora.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/65/Johanna_Lannister_Hylora.jpg/700px-Johanna_Lannister_Hylora.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>Johanna Lannister by © Hylora</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nJohanna Westerling</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Titles</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li>Lady of <a href=\"/index.php/Casterly_Rock\" title=\"Casterly Rock\">Casterly Rock</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabaftermath_-_the_hour_of_the_wolf.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabaftermath_-_the_hour_of_the_wolf.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Regent\" title=\"Regent\">Regent</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabaftermath_-_the_hour_of_the_wolf.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabaftermath_-_the_hour_of_the_wolf.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Westerling\" title=\"House Westerling\">House Westerling</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">House Lannister</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Westermen\" title=\"Westermen\">Westermen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Father</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Roland_Westerling\" title=\"Roland Westerling\">Roland Westerling</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Spouse</th><td>\nLord <a href=\"/index.php/Jason_Lannister\" title=\"Jason Lannister\">Jason Lannister</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Issue</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Cerelle_Lannister_(daughter_of_Jason)\" title=\"Cerelle Lannister (daughter of Jason)\">Cerelle Lannister</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Tyshara_Lannister\" title=\"Tyshara Lannister\">Tyshara Lannister</a></li><li>3 other daughters</li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Loreon_Lannister_(son_of_Jason)\" title=\"Loreon Lannister (son of Jason)\">Loreon Lannister</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rise_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Rise of the Dragon\">The Rise of the Dragon</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Johanna Lannister</b>, née <b>Westerling</b>, was the Lady of <a href=\"/index.php/Casterly_Rock\" title=\"Casterly Rock\">Casterly Rock</a> through her <a href=\"/index.php/Marriage\" title=\"Marriage\">marriage</a> to Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Jason_Lannister\" title=\"Jason Lannister\">Jason Lannister</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_the_red_kraken.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_the_red_kraken.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Johanna_Lannister&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Lady Johanna was the daughter of <a href=\"/index.php/Roland_Westerling\" title=\"Roland Westerling\">Roland Westerling</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_the_Crag\" title=\"Lord of the Crag\">Lord of the Crag</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabaftermath_-_the_hour_of_the_wolf.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabaftermath_-_the_hour_of_the_wolf.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>During the civil war known as the <a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a>, Johanna's husband, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Jason_Lannister\" title=\"Jason Lannister\">Jason Lannister</a>, and his twin brother, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Tyland_Lannister\" title=\"Tyland Lannister\">Tyland</a>, supported the <a href=\"/index.php/Greens\" title=\"Greens\">greens</a>. Jason led his <a href=\"/index.php/Bannerman\" title=\"Bannerman\">banners</a> and marched to the field in support of King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon II Targaryen\">Aegon II Targaryen</a>, but he was slain in the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_at_the_Red_Fork\" title=\"Battle at the Red Fork\">Battle at the Red Fork</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/130_AC\" title=\"130 AC\">130&#160;AC</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_targaryen_kings:_aegon_ii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_targaryen_kings:_aegon_ii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> After Jason's death, Johanna ruled <a href=\"/index.php/Casterly_Rock\" title=\"Casterly Rock\">Casterly Rock</a> as a <a href=\"/index.php/Regent\" title=\"Regent\">regent</a> for their young son, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Loreon_Lannister\" title=\"Loreon Lannister\">Loreon Lannister</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabaftermath_-_the_hour_of_the_wolf.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabaftermath_-_the_hour_of_the_wolf.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> <a href=\"/index.php/Dalton_Greyjoy\" title=\"Dalton Greyjoy\">Dalton Greyjoy</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_the_Iron_Islands\" title=\"Lord of the Iron Islands\">Lord of the Iron Islands</a>, took advantage of the situation and attacked the <a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">westerlands</a>, causing much damage to the region. Lady Johanna barred the gates of the Rock, but the Red Kraken captured most of the <a href=\"/index.php/Lannister_fleet\" title=\"Lannister fleet\">Lannister fleet</a>, burned the rest, and sacked nearby <a href=\"/index.php/Lannisport\" title=\"Lannisport\">Lannisport</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_red_dragon_and_the_gold.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_red_dragon_and_the_gold.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>As one of the <a href=\"/index.php/Three_Widows\" title=\"Three Widows\">Three Widows</a>, Johanna agreed to make peace with the <a href=\"/index.php/Blacks\" title=\"Blacks\">blacks</a> after the death of Aegon II in return for the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Throne\" title=\"Iron Throne\">Iron Throne</a> ordering Dalton to return to the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Islands\" title=\"Iron Islands\">Iron Islands</a>, free <a href=\"/index.php/Fair_Isle\" title=\"Fair Isle\">Fair Isle</a>, and return all captured women.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabaftermath_-_the_hour_of_the_wolf.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabaftermath_-_the_hour_of_the_wolf.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> Johanna and her father attended the wedding of King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_III_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon III Targaryen\">Aegon III Targaryen</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaera_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaera Targaryen\">Jaehaera Targaryen</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Dalton ignored the commands of the <a href=\"/index.php/Regency_of_Aegon_III\" title=\"Regency of Aegon III\">regency of Aegon III</a> to vacate the <a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">westerlands</a>. When Johanna began building a new fleet of warships, Dalton attacked the shipyards and captured another hundred women.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Johanna donned mail to lead the remaining Lannister forces in the struggle to drive the ironborn from their shores.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> Leading a host from Casterly Rock and Lannisport, Johanna routed the ironborn beneath <a href=\"/index.php/Kayce\" title=\"Kayce\">Kayce</a>'s walls, with Dalton's uncle slain in the fighting. Songs claim Johanna slew twelve ironmen in the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_at_Kayce\" title=\"Battle at Kayce\">battle at Kayce</a>, although scholars believe she only carried a banner.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> Johanna next arranged an expedition to recover Fair Isle, but her plan was betrayed to the ironborn. The ragtag fleet sent by the regent was destroyed in an <a href=\"/index.php/Ambush_at_Fair_Isle\" title=\"Ambush at Fair Isle\">ambush at Fair Isle</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>There was a <a href=\"/index.php/Struggle_for_power\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Struggle for power\">struggle for power</a> among the ironborn after the Red Kraken was murdered at <a href=\"/index.php/Faircastle\" title=\"Faircastle\">Faircastle</a> a few years later. Since the Lannister fleet had been destroyed by the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Greyjoy\" title=\"House Greyjoy\">Greyjoys</a>, Johanna allied with the <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_admiral\" title=\"Lord admiral\">lord admiral</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a>, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Leo_Costayne\" title=\"Leo Costayne\">Leo Costayne</a>, to have the westermen invade the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Islands\" title=\"Iron Islands\">Iron Islands</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/134_AC\" title=\"134 AC\">134&#160;AC</a>. When <a href=\"/index.php/Rodrik_Greyjoy_(son_of_Dalton)\" title=\"Rodrik Greyjoy (son of Dalton)\">Rodrik Greyjoy</a> was taken to Casterly Rock as a captive, Johanna had him <a href=\"/index.php/Eunuch\" title=\"Eunuch\">gelded</a> and made him her son's <a href=\"/index.php/Fool\" title=\"Fool\">fool</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_the_red_kraken.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_the_red_kraken.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Johanna reclaimed the dwindling glory of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">House Lannister</a> and also lent gold to <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> to help rebuild the extensive damages caused by the previous civil war.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Johanna_Lannister&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Roland_Westerling\" title=\"Roland Westerling\">Roland</a></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\">Unknown<br />wife</td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"